   352→/**
   353→ *  Very naive TF-IDF style scoring.  In production use, replace with proper
   354→ *  full-text search (PostgreSQL tsvector/tsquery or Elasticsearch), but this
   355→ *  algorithm is serviceable for demo purposes without extra dependencies.
   356→ */
   357→double score_document(std::string_view text,
   358→                      const std::vector<std::string>& search_terms)
   359→{
   360→    if (search_terms.empty())
